sorry i havent been updating, ive been super busy and it seems to only get worse. haha well the tennis season should be ending soon and that should free up time. but anyways, i went the the lax game today to watch a certian sum1 play hehe i got to chill wit maria too since she showed up after my constant begging! hehe i owe her big time as she says. i also hung out with her on friday to saturday. we were at franks until like 2 in the morning, but it was fun all the same! my parents are going out of town this weekend and i am gonna be with the G-Rents so holla at my fone if u need me. i assure you i wont be busy at all...haha

COME TO THE FRICKIN' TENNIS MATCH TOMORROW!!! 330-6 BE THERE OR BE SQUARE!!!





today was a pleasently boring day, just normal school as it should be without my normal drama! there was no tennis today, which was cool b.c i havent not had tennis in a while, normally it takes up LOTS of time and i never get to talk to my hommies!! haha o yeah we won yesterday that makes us 8-3. we play south carroll tomorrow at home EVERYONE HAS TO GO!!!! we need sum more spectaters!!! all we have is ourselves...not that thats s bad thing, but still... but anyways today is CJs birthday and mom is in VA cleaning for a KIK ASS weekend ahead of us!! haha i mean you cant go wrong with james, casey, landy, and girlie (caroline) PLUS special guest EMMA! woohoo so yeah i am excited about thatttttttt! 


(not necessary to read the bottom...u can if u want to tho.)

i have a craving...............................for a boy!! i usually dont go a month w.o one!! hehe "for as long as ive known you, i havent seen you go a month without a boy." -emma its been like what 3 months or so since bryan? and nope, no boys. not even a "friends with benefits" its not like im all "hung up" on him. b.c ive been done with him for a good 3 months, at least (sorry). it makes me happy knowing how much freedom i have w.o him. but then i liked having the security of having sumone to run to all the time. and i dont rele have that any more. i cant even turn to him as a friend anymore, as he wont talk to me. hell he wont even tell me whats going on in his life and he has to lie about EVERYTHING!!! o well i want a boy!!! i want him to be sweet, caring, and HOTT! hehe i rele want a hott boy!! hehe a boy thats into my EXACT music taste (hehe ud get that if u knew who i was kinda crushin') would be nice!! aiight well im out time to make dinner, as mom is in VA.... :-/


TENNIS TOMORROW!!! ITS A MUST!!!

i dont like that one freak anymore so i dont rele care about the stupid skank!!! hehe and the best part of my day is practice got cut short!!!! it was great!!! and since speck wasent there we didnt run at all!!! it was all great greatness until mom started yelling at me and my brother called me a "frickin critic" when i told him ot turn his music down (it was sooo loud i could hear it when i was vacuuming). i hope it gets better from here!!! thank you daniela for fixing my lj and making it PRETTY!!!!! hehe well im out. wish us luck on our match tomorrow against FSK!!! (i dont think well need it too bad tho...hehe) o and if you feel like it, come to the game on FrIdAy, its a home game against south carroll, it should be a good one! 

pe@ce ouT

i had a blast yesterday playing tennis with danielle!! it was soo much fun. she beat me 4-6, but it was close until i got lazy. haha coach wouldnt have liked that...o well now ill be better if i play tomorrow well im gonna go down to chris's bye bye!!

wow livejournal has not been something to do lately has it?

well week in summary

TENNIS- we lost monday, won wednesday, lost today....

BOYS-lets not go there

SCHOOL-midterms/finals sucked, i didnt do too bad tho...my quarter grades are BBAA, maybe BAAA...i have no idea

i think that sums it up, well from a summary standpoint it does....

what a busy weekend...
FRIDAY~tennis against middletown. it was the best game i have ever watched (no exhibition played, they only had one player and coach needed us to cheer) then we get home to century and wow my parents are out at dinner that they never told me about...so i bummed a ride home with devin
SATURDAY(my 15th BIRTHDAY!)~ p2p meeting we came a half hour late...smooth...but it was a good meeting, i got to meet/bond with people on the trip. we had community service after the meeting and it only took an hour or so and so we all hung out afterwards. then i came home for a few hours and then i went and babysat landy and girly (caroline). i spent the night over there because no one could drive me home, if you get the drift...
SUNDAY~i left the Reeve's house around 10 and came home for a few hours only to leave again for bball. we played girls against parents, which was fun. we only lost by 2 points hehe. then i came home agian for a few hours until we left and went to Cal. T. for dinner. then we came home and ate pie and opned present, i got my BIG one earlier. now i am sitting here. i think ill do sum homework

<3me

i am sitting here
it seems to be it
on top of the world
looking down on everything

all the chaos
all the hate
all the love 
all the peace

why am i not there?
i am all alone
cant i get help?
i look at you
and i fall back down
back to everything

all the chaos
all the hate
all the love
all the peace...

<3me
i really want some of tim's cake....not that anyone understands the need for it....
i lost...it sums it up....o and some one i like...is liked by someone that knew i liked him....shes actually doing shit about it...no...just no....

i am gonna be sooo out of it with the whole clock changing thing...ive never been god at it. *sigh* i have a bball game at 2, i really dont feel like playing. but then after that emily is coming over to finishour project...thats gonna take foooooorever. my stupid parents were all not coming home last night so we couldnt do it yesterday. 

o well.

tennis was groovay yesterday, we won against winters mill, man we kiked their ass! it was 5-love both sides! woot hoo!! the bus was awesome too, we were all hyper, it think we scared tim...but thats okay, im sure hell get used to it. but yeah then was emmas party, it was groovay! we did finger paint and then made those funky iron bead things!! twas greatness okay my madre is pushing me out the door, off to walmart!!! yahoo!
im in the media center working on a project for GP with Emily...our game is gonna rock!! ive got practice later so i wont be home for a while...its all rainy and gross outside...ewww

i dont like being back at school. no bueno... i miss sleeping in til 9 and hanging around until 12. i also miss my other house. its so nice to wake up in the morning and looking out the window at beautiful woods, and sometimes getting a glimpse of the lake. *sigh* its nice to be back into tennis tho. we had a game yesterday. i actually played! chloe and i lost tho, 3-6. i was okay tho, it was our first so we still have time to improve, even tho it is exibition. tennis today was cool, just hitting the ball again was cool. i stink...i need a shower, but ill shower after dinner. il make the family suffer... hehe oo yeah bridget was @ the school and i got to see her which was cool since i only see her like once in a blue moon. (there have been alot of blue moons lately...) i took a picture of her with my new camera!! hehe i am so happy about it! its sooo pretty!! hehe okay im out...bye

i went to go walk in the rain and i go outside to find there is no rain to walk in. so i went for a walk in the mist...not at all as fun. plus it was by myself. even less fun. that makes me think about things, and thats never good. but if bri or keegan went with me it would have been much more enjoyabe. but no bri is stupid and is out of town. and i have no idea where keegan is. maybe an evening walk will be good...who knows...

i am sooo happy it is here!!! i have missed it!!!
it makes me happy...

back from Bryce...as of like 6 oclock. it was a groovay weekend. we got there thursday around lunch...very boring afternoon, i mostly read...like the nerd i am. there isnt much to do anyway..we have no TV no computer and it was raining so it limited my options. then on friday we lunged around, cj, dad, and i went on a drive and we went to this amazing town. its sooo pretty. the buildings are amazing. the main building is a hotel and its the biggest hotel i have ever seen in my life! we asked our nighbor (who came over for dinner that night) about it and he said u can rent the cabins around the hotel, but he didnt know about the hotel, if it was for big things or what. he also said they have a big music festival in the summer. that would be fun to go to. but then my grandparents and my uncle and his GF came down and we got to hang with them all day which was our "easter", since we wouldnt have one being all in the wilderness and all ;) and then our easter today consisted of french toast and peeps and choclate....the easter bunny slacked this year... idc tho...it gave us a new house!! hehe well yeah so much of a spring break huh??

bri is soo cool. she fixed my live journal and made it useable. now i am not embarassed to be seen with it looking the way it did...spring break is ON! its gonna be cool. it started out awesome, i mean who doesnt love hanging with BRIANNE!!!! twas greatness. i love playing in the RAIN!! i hope the rest of the break will be this cool...expeciallly down in BRYCE!! i hope to meet some peeps down at the house. i doubt we will, but who cares. i get MORE quality time with the folks. like i havent spent enough time with them lately... luckily my mom went to the library so ill have "quality reading" for my alone time... i wishi had my cell fone now, then i wouldnt be secluded for a week. but o well, ill steal my dads....haha im a rebel!!! ok im out...peace <3tye

We'll start a new life

All I know is that I love you tonight 
There was

The rain came down so hard that night and the 
Headlines read

No tell-tale heart was left to find when you...

so basically back when they were good.
*sigh*

i want school

my classes are cooler *hotter boys!*

ugly girls who think im sooo hott.

she deserves the sleep
doing half of the work she does
everyday wore me out, i can imagine doing
it every fucking day! geez!
o well i stil have a good twenty years
until i have to get used to it
erg...
